:"The thumbnail type to generate all possible thumbnail representations."},{"t":"cancel(_:)","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailGenerator/cancel(_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Cancels the generation of a thumbnail for a given request."},{"t":"cgImage","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailRepresentation/cgImage","r":"Instance Property","a":"A thumbnail in the form of a Core Graphics image object."},{"t":"contentRect","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailRepresentation/contentRect","r":"Instance Property","a":"The rectangle within the thumbnail image of the document that represents its contents."},{"t":"contentType","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailGenerator/Request/contentType","r":"Instance Property","a":"The content type of the source data for the thumbnail request."},{"t":"errorDomain","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailError-swift.struct/errorDomain","r":"Type Property"},{"t":"extensionBadge","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailReply/extensionBadge","r":"Instance Property","a":"A short string that identifies the file type that the system uses as a badge when producing an icon thumbnail."},{"t":"fileURL","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLFileThumbnailRequest/fileURL","r":"Instance Property","a":"The URL of the image file to use for the thumbnail."},{"t":"generateBestRepresentation(for:completion:)","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailGenerator/generateBestRepresentation(for:completion:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Generates the best possible thumbnail representation for a file and calls a handler upon completion."},{"t":"generateRepresentations(for:update:)","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailGenerator/generateRepresentations(for:update:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Generates various thumbnail representations for a file and calls the update handler for each thumbnail representation."},{"t":"generationFailed","p":"documentati