e form of an AppKit image object."},{"t":"provideThumbnail(for:_:)","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailProvider/provideThumbnail(for:_:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Creates a thumbnail of a custom file type for a specific request."},{"t":"representationTypes","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailGenerator/Request/representationTypes-swift.property","r":"Instance Property","a":"The thumbnail sizes that you provide for a thumbnail request."},{"t":"requestCancelled","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailError-swift.struct/requestCancelled","r":"Type Property","a":"The request to create a thumbnail was canceled."},{"t":"requestInvalid","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailError-swift.struct/requestInvalid","r":"Type Property","a":"The request to create a thumbnail was invalid, for example, there\u2019s no file at a provided URL."},{"t":"saveBestRepresentation(for:to:as:completion:)","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailGenerator/saveBestRepresentation(for:to:as:completion:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Saves a thumbnail for the request on disk at fileURL. The file saved at fileURL has to be deleted when it is not used anymore. This is primarily intended for file provider extensions which need to upload thumbnails and have a small memory limit."},{"t":"saveBestRepresentation(for:to:contentType:completion:)","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailGenerator/saveBestRepresentation(for:to:contentType:completion:)","r":"Instance Method","a":"Saves the best representation of thumbnail for a specific request to the specified URL."},{"t":"savingToURLFailed","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLThumbnailError-swift.struct/savingToURLFailed","r":"Type Property","a":"The thumbnail couldn\u2019t be saved at the given URL."},{"t":"scale","p":"documentation/QuickLookThumbnailing/QLFileThumbnailRequest/scale","r":"Instance Property","a":"The scale of the requested thumbnail."},{"t":"scale","p"